Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.72,0:02:01.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H575F66&\4c&H575F66&\pos(640,504)\blur3\1c&HCCD4DD&}Wolf and Enticing Traveler
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.40,0:01:49.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.40,0:01:52.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I could watch this all day!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.10,0:02:05.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We ended up doing this after all, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.26,0:02:12.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Though from here, it doesn't look like the city's having any particular problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.71,0:02:16.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when wolf packs are having a violent war over territory,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.35,0:02:21.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,the forest looks as calm as it always does from a distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.45,0:02:28.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even you can't tell with your eyes or ears from afar?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.86,0:02:30.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,See them over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.07,0:02:34.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The tax on the goods they're shipping is ridiculously high,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.30,0:02:37.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and they're saying they don't want to hand over the goods at the original price.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.82,0:02:40.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Something or other about the price per head.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.18,0:02:42.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A hostage tax, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.37,0:02:47.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good cargo might as well be hostage to the owner of the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:50.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And now the thin one is saying:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.60,0:02:55.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"The town is in heavy dispute because of the Northern expedition being canceled."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.52,0:02:58.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"You should be happy you can even get paid."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.08,0:03:02.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The cancellation of the Northern expedition is having effects even here, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.90,0:03:05.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"If you want, you can bet on the meeting outcome with your furs." { FOTC: "If you want, you can bet on the meeting with your furs." }
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.38,0:03:11.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There are at least four other groups of people having similar discussions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:13.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Taxes too high.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:15.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Northern expedition.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.44,0:03:17.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How imports are trending in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.83,0:03:22.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:27.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The wine you just ordered isn't for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.94,0:03:29.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but for yourself, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:34.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting drunk on wine, but something else is making you drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.43,0:03:37.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You need money to drink wine,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:42.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but thinking of ways to make profit is free.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:45.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But we haven't just been idly chatting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:51.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,One or two mugs for the possibility of me lending you help in earnest is a cheap price.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:54.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It is as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.69,0:04:00.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you really do look like you're having fun when you talk about business.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:02.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take that face as an appetizer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.79,0:04:07.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:12.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone like me, in this state after wine of that grade? {LAWRENCE, WHAT DOES THE SCOUTER SAY ABOUT ITS POWER LEVEL!?!?!?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.39,0:04:15.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're probably tired from the journey too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:16.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Rest for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.65,0:04:22.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:23.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm too expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.62,0:04:24.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No one will want to buy me. {He admitted it!!}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.88,0:04:27.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.80,0:04:32.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Rest well, princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.49,0:04:46.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you open?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:50.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I just finished patching up the hole. { FOTC: Pun on the bar closing? "I was just closing up." }
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:53.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.38,0:04:56.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to look till I bore another hole through it. { is that... a really lame way of hitting on her? } { Of course I'd let him fuck me for that. }
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:04:58.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:05:03.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever a hole appears in my apron, everyone stops looking at my face and just stares at the apron.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.51,0:05:06.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's just being careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.13,0:05:10.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They're afraid if they look at your beautiful face too much, they'll bore a third hole into your nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.82,0:05:12.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:16.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had three, it'd be easier to tell apart customers that smell bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.92,0:05:18.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How am I, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.89,0:05:26.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Traveling customers really do catch onto jokes differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:28.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, will it be a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.78,0:05:29.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Or food?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.41,0:05:34.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Could I get two of the tail dishes packaged up for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.68,0:05:39.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now the chef's preparing food for the dock workers...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.73,0:05:41.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.73,0:05:43.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:44.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.47,0:05:47.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,how about having a drink while you're waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:50.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.65,0:05:59.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Traveling merchants who come to a bar at this time of day have one objective in mind, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.37,0:06:01.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Before that, let me pay...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:07.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I just noticed in passing,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:10.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but there's a lot of merchants hanging around the city entrance, aren't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:11.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.49,0:06:15.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,the ones selling furs and fur-related merchandise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.56,0:06:17.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Furs?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:20.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The furs, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.80,0:06:24.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Half of them are merchants who've come here from faraway countries hoping to sell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.87,0:06:30.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The other half are selling tools and wares needed to process the fur into other goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.07,0:06:32.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And you probably want to know why they're all hanging around there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.97,0:06:37.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, the higher ups of the town are deciding whether or not to allow fur to be sold.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:39.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This Fifty-man meeting thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.49,0:06:40.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.64,0:06:43.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,While that's going on, fur trade is prohibited.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.82,0:06:49.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That being the case, all the craftsmen aren't sure whether to buy the goods needed to process fur or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.05,0:06:52.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the reason they're deliberating over its sale in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.45,0:06:56.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it's because the Northern expedition was canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.36,0:07:00.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The people who'd buy up fur in bulk are all gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.57,0:07:01.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.45,0:07:05.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Usually I'd have a lot more customers here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.54,0:07:10.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't they just sell their fur to the merchants at the city gates?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:17.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all pretty stingy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:20.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Knights and mercenaries on the other hand are quite generous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.61,0:07:27.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes I even receive fancy clothes like the noblewomen wear as gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:30.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, they're very expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.40,0:07:34.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But the cost of furs before they're made into clothes is ridiculously cheap. {スルーされた　Σ(￣Д￣;)}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.60,0:07:39.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If they aren't sold and made into clothes, the city's income will drop quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.21,0:07:40.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.30,0:07:46.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But any barmaid in town can tell you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.32,0:07:51.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretend you didn't hear what I'm about to tell you. {Even assuming she's wearing a bra, that coin's still gonna go right down her dress.} { FOTC: It'll lodge into the apron. They're most comfortable when tightly tied. }
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.73,0:07:53.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.39,0:08:07.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that in all likelihood, they'll prevent the merchants outside from purchasing the fur.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.28,0:08:12.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though they know it'll anger the craftsmen and the fur handlers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:13.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your source for this? {CITATION NEEDED} { SRC PLZ GPL THX }
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:16.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.07,0:08:20.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Patrons will always leave a good bar drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.99,0:08:23.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be nice if you were the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:26.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The drink will be hitting me pretty soon. { FOTC: "alcohol" -> "drunkenness" }
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:28.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The tail dish is done!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:30.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.62,0:08:32.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:34.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,do you have a wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:40.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She hasn't gotten a hold of my purse yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.65,0:08:44.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but she has a firm hold over my reins.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.03,0:08:49.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She must be a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:51.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.37,0:09:01.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Those contain furs, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.75,0:09:02.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Those do too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:05.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And those.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.82,0:09:07.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And those.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.15,0:09:09.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.99,0:09:11.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,the amount of money involved here must be huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.23,0:09:15.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.70,0:09:18.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't sell my tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.43,0:09:23.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.28,0:09:26.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face says you're ready to sell anything that can be sold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.35,0:09:29.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.81,0:09:34.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,For instance, I wouldn't try to sell a strawberry growing on the side of the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.01,0:09:38.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I buy goods from one person and sell to another.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:40.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That is an unbreakable principle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:44.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what gossip have you heard about this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:48.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This time it's another exceptionally interesting story.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.19,0:09:50.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:51.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to play a game?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:53.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A game?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.04,0:09:56.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can figure out what kind of animal and what part of it this is using just your nose,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.96,0:09:59.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you have anything you like for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.35,0:10:02.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh really. {ORLY}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:08.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember those merchants who were hanging around the town entrance?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.63,0:10:10.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There has to be a reason for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.12,0:10:14.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They wouldn't be waiting around like that if there weren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.37,0:10:20.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely, they think that at the end of the meeting,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.83,0:10:22.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,foreign trade will continue to be barred.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.50,0:10:26.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not thinking of opening the package, are you? { FOTC: 立派な尻尾だな }
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.01,0:10:30.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.57,0:10:31.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Figure it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.82,0:10:32.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.54,0:10:35.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Back to the subject,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.02,0:10:39.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no mistake — some major political power is pulling strings in the background.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.26,0:10:43.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Some western merchant organization known for clothing materials?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:48.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A big company trying to attain a monopoly in the fur business?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.66,0:10:49.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.91,0:10:51.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Lawrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:52.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Figure it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:11:00.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think guessing wouldn't go well under your conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.09,0:11:03.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to say that before you start.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.98,0:11:06.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well that's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:08.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So? Your answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.10,0:11:10.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the name,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.67,0:11:15.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's the tail of a rodent with a big, flat tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.10,0:11:21.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I said it wouldn't go well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:22.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:24.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When we came to this town,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.25,0:11:28.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I had an uneasy feeling because I couldn't place this smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.55,0:11:30.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.51,0:11:34.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My memories of it came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.61,0:11:41.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The game was really whether I could stop myself from crying from the nostalgia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.26,0:11:47.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you do it on purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.59,0:11:51.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I'd take advantage of someone's goodwill?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.86,0:11:54.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always taking advantage of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.10,0:12:10.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never forget this scent either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,0:12:14.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.64,0:12:19.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It smells fishy coming from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.04,0:12:20.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.87,0:12:25.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you that troubled?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.28,0:12:30.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,With the money from Kumerson, you could easily set up a shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.24,0:12:33.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.72,0:12:40.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no right to stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.62,0:12:43.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not worried, why not relax a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:46.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.37,0:12:52.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.47,0:12:54.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's also true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.92,0:13:06.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Roads to the north?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:07.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.35,0:13:10.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There was little snow this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.61,0:13:13.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It shouldn't be too difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.45,0:13:16.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm heading towards Niohira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.86,0:13:19.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're purposely going to the heathen lands?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.84,0:13:25.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess that's what a merchant does.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.01,0:13:30.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Go anywhere to fill their bag of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.29,0:13:35.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But when we die in the end, we throw away that bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.38,0:13:38.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why do you labor for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.31,0:13:41.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,To obtain it, just to throw it away?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.51,0:13:46.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't ask the same question when you clean your home. {OOOHHHH BUUUURN!} { SOME LIKE IT HOT http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eLW5jzHsW7c }
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:51.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{ Hmph. } Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:53.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be leaving soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.99,0:13:55.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.06,0:13:58.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll stay until the Fifty-man meeting ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.38,0:14:03.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you left now, you'd probably make it halfway there on your horse before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.50,0:14:06.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it'd be better if you rode a long-haired breed instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.98,0:14:09.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one in the stable, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.04,0:14:12.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Its owner is a man from the north.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.03,0:14:15.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He should know the road conditions well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.26,0:14:16.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,His name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.81,0:14:17.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.51,0:14:22.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's long stayed here, but I've never asked his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.72,0:14:27.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I remember him growing fatter with the years.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.80,0:14:30.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.17,0:14:32.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,These things happen as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.75,0:14:40.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll mention you if I see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.01,0:14:41.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.39,0:14:48.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you stay for the Fifty-man meeting, you might regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.33,0:14:50.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Will it go on that long?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:59.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There are many trends in a man's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.69,0:15:04.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So in a town where many lives gather, there must be trends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.28,0:15:10.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's a trend of man to fight fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.62,0:15:14.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I commit a sin, I will repent like a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.52,0:15:24.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hard to object to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.05,0:15:27.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your third night here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.66,0:15:28.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:31.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Craft Lawrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.06,0:15:33.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Harold Ekrund.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.56,0:15:36.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was younger, I would burn out the night talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.34,0:15:41.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But these days I enjoy my quiet nights.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.49,0:15:43.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's most important.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.82,0:15:45.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,For me it was the fifth night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.18,0:15:49.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You would talk to him sooner than you would me, Harold?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.21,0:15:53.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My first talk with you was on your fifth night, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.91,0:15:57.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's rare for you to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.21,0:15:59.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.04,0:16:01.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.32,0:16:03.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we have a chat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:05.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You have some business with Rigolo, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.08,0:16:08.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.22,0:16:10.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking this. {mah booooze...}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.10,0:16:13.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.01,0:16:21.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What a waste to warm this wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.12,0:16:24.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be wary of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.93,0:16:26.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.31,0:16:29.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because female merchants are rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.39,0:16:34.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If one were to talk to me, I'd be more cautious than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.35,0:16:39.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,These few years, no one's ever seen through me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.08,0:16:43.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This morning, we passed each other outside the inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.63,0:16:46.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My companion's animal-like instincts picked up on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.42,0:16:50.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't fool a woman's intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.49,0:16:52.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I can't say so myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:54.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel the same way every d- {em dash pls}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.67,0:16:58.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Fruhl Boland.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:01.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't let my name restrict me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.44,0:17:03.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,For business, it's Abe Boland.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.92,0:17:05.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Craft Lawrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.47,0:17:07.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Craft? Lawrence?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.51,0:17:09.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In business, it's Lawrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:12.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Abe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:14.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like the Boland much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:15.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Also,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.47,0:17:21.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how my face looks to a man when I use make up and put up my hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.03,0:17:24.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't like the praise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:26.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.53,0:17:28.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could hide it, I would hide it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.96,0:17:31.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm not as modest as I might seem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:34.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a talker, if I say so myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.89,0:17:37.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll brag about how I'm actually quite sociable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.18,0:17:42.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your sociability is gradually making an impression on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.12,0:17:44.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.93,0:17:48.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,we haven't exchanged anything but short greetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.53,0:17:50.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see why you've taken to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.22,0:17:55.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,One reason is that old man Harold's taken to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.27,0:17:58.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That geezer's got good eyes for people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.60,0:18:00.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Though he's reserved and unsociable.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.12,0:18:03.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And his favorite phrase is,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.13,0:18:06.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Next year I'll go on a pilgrimage."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.54,0:18:11.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What about your companion?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.44,0:18:11.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My companion?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.95,0:18:13.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, your companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.68,0:18:16.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.44,0:18:19.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't see many merchants with female companions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.07,0:18:22.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there's quite a bit about my companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.36,0:18:24.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I don't mean to pry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:30.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You two look like you've traveled quite a bit, and you don't seem to be bound by money.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:34.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought that I could talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.67,0:18:37.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's how it was,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.68,0:18:40.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but to come out of the blue with "How about we make some small talk?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.02,0:18:41.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I could just say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.85,0:18:44.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So I used Rigolo's name,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:47.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but it wasn't just a way to pull you out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:50.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to meet Rigolo, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.85,0:18:53.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.00,0:18:55.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,May I inquire as to your reasons?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.05,0:19:00.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that Rigolo is this town's chronicler.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.09,0:19:03.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see records of old stories of this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.49,0:19:07.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite a strange reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.19,0:19:10.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought for sure you wanted to talk about furs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.87,0:19:13.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I am a merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.32,0:19:16.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't hurt to have some information about that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.62,0:19:18.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's dangerous,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.90,0:19:21.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and my companion doesn't wish for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.74,0:19:28.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He does have a mountain of books passed down through the generations in his study,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.26,0:19:32.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and it does seem like his dream is to pass his days reading them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.27,0:19:37.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He wants to retire from being the scribe at the Fifty-man Meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:38.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.65,0:19:43.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no end to the people who want to get close to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.67,0:19:49.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you went to see him now, he'd probably just glare at you and turn you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:52.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trading with the Church in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.59,0:19:55.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have quite a relation with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.20,0:20:00.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And usually Rigolo writes things for the Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.03,0:20:03.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that connection, we've known each other for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.83,0:20:06.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Merchant Lawrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.52,0:20:09.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if you're a great man or whatever,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.81,0:20:13.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but you do seem a bit different from the rabble around us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.73,0:20:16.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very kind of you to praise me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.81,0:20:20.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but can you wait a little longer before we shake hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.85,0:20:24.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not the kind to have sweaty palms.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.63,0:20:28.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been wearing that unreadable mask for some time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.15,0:20:34.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then instead of asking about what you trade, can I ask something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.65,0:20:35.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.26,0:20:38.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What would it cost to introduce me to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.24,0:20:43.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need money or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.31,0:20:45.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.62,0:20:51.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you chat with me? { やる. 「俺」をやめるなら。女らしくない　(　┰_┰) シクシク} { 男か女かなど関係ない. やる. } { SOME LIKE IT HOT http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eLW5jzHsW7c }
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.32,0:20:56.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What, I'm not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.85,0:20:59.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You may think it strange,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.44,0:21:04.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but to me, having someone to talk to without needing to hide my gender,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.83,0:21:08.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,especially another merchant, is worth more than Lima gold coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.99,0:21:12.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's worth less than Lumione silver. { FOTC: I think "but" works too. }
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.15,0:21:15.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.35,0:21:17.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, money is most valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.00,0:21:21.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.25,0:21:23.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what kind of person your companion is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.83,0:21:25.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could, I'd like to talk to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.64,0:21:28.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but when someone gives you the cold shoulder, wine tastes bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.17,0:21:31.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think she would.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.43,0:21:32.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.69,0:21:35.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing you can understand less than a woman's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.64,0:21:38.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't understand woman talk anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.14,0:21:44.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I am here to do business. {Lawrence gets poked in the face by women a lot. Wonder if that means something...} { He likes getting face fucked. }
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.19,0:21:47.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If it works out, I'd like someone to talk with.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.36,0:21:49.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I may not look it, but I'm—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:51.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A talker and a sociable person.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.74,0:21:57.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.86,0:22:00.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as my companion doesn't get envious.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.35,0:22:03.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a difficult condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.10,0:23:52.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Wolf and Careless Negotiations
